    "However, directly using the text decoder as a multimodal decoder, may lead to significant mismatching between the image encoding space and the decoder input space.",
    "Therefore, to further fill the gap between the image embedding space, here, we pre-train the whole network with the PMC-OA 13 dataset by captioning each image, which is similar to BLIP-2 15.",
